Package eventdetection.downloader

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Downloader
    This represents an object that can download information from news sources.
    DownloaderCollection
    Implements a Downloader that queries a list of other Downloaders and returns the RawArticles that they find.
    DownloaderController  
    Feed
    Represents an RSS feed and provides methods for getting the articles from it.
    FeedManager
    A system for loading and managing Feeds and Scrapers.
    RawArticle
    Contains the contents of a single article
    Scraper
    A mechanism for scraping article text from online sources
